proximity to the place

00:07:40.440 --> 00:07:46.170 align:middle line:84%
where atomic bombs were
detonated between 1945 and '48.

00:07:46.170 --> 00:07:49.080 align:middle line:84%
It's not by chance that
these alien visitors

00:07:49.080 --> 00:07:51.930 align:middle line:84%
had been so interested
in the new technology

00:07:51.930 --> 00:07:54.705 align:middle line:84%
that human beings had
developed for war purposes.

00:07:54.705 --> 00:07:57.560 align:middle line:90%


00:07:57.560 --> 00:08:02.470 align:middle line:84%
>> How far are we
hear from Los Alamos,

00:08:02.470 --> 00:08:07.156 align:middle line:84%
