00:08:07.156 --> 00:08:08.900 align:middle line:90%
>> See those bumpy hills there?

00:08:08.900 --> 00:08:09.700 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:08:09.700 --> 00:08:12.180 align:middle line:90%
