00:08:37.346 --> 00:08:40.809 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, from where the
bomb was, it's 18 miles.

00:08:40.809 --> 00:08:41.919 align:middle line:90%
>> 18 miles?

00:08:41.919 --> 00:08:44.384 align:middle line:90%
>> 18 miles.

00:08:44.384 --> 00:08:45.670 align:middle line:90%
>> It's too close, isn't it?

00:08:45.670 --> 00:08:50.230 align:middle line:90%


00:08:50.230 --> 00:08:51.930 align:middle line:90%
>> It is too close.

00:08:51.930 --> 00:08:53.820 align:middle line:90%
Because that's when my mother--

00:08:53.820 --> 00:08:56.770 align:middle line:84%
