00:09:15.090 --> 00:09:15.940 align:middle line:90%
this way.

00:09:15.940 --> 00:09:18.548 align:middle line:90%
That was the radiation.

00:09:18.548 --> 00:09:19.955 align:middle line:90%
>> You were hit by it?

00:09:19.955 --> 00:09:23.060 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh yes.

00:09:23.060 --> 00:09:25.980 align:middle line:10%
We felt it, it was
warm, like a warm--

00:09:25.980 --> 00:09:28.900 align:middle line:10%
not this fast, you know?

00:09:28.900 --> 00:09:32.752 align:middle line:10%
But there was like a warm
wind coming through then.

00:09:32.752 --> 00:09:34.320 align:middle line:10%
>> And your mother?

00:09:34.320 --> 00:09:36.810 align:middle line:84%
>> My mother lost the sight
of that eye, you know?

00:09:36.810 --> 00:09:37.990 align:middle line:90%
She was looking at that.

00:09:37.990 --> 00:09:44.790 align:middle line:84%
But she lost it from the
