>> Just burned.

00:09:48.240 --> 00:09:51.900 align:middle line:84%
Well, no I jumped
underneath the bed.

00:09:51.900 --> 00:09:54.240 align:middle line:84%
Then about three minutes
later, I came out.

00:09:54.240 --> 00:09:57.870 align:middle line:84%
That's when everything
