I guess they were
checking out, seeing

00:10:05.850 --> 00:10:09.746 align:middle line:90%
if there was any damage here.

00:10:09.746 --> 00:10:13.520 align:middle line:10%
>> How did you feel then?

00:10:13.520 --> 00:10:25.487 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, I just felt a strong
blow and the light of it.

