00:28:54.890 --> 00:28:57.640 align:middle line:90%
but for airplanes in flight.

00:28:57.640 --> 00:29:01.390 align:middle line:10%
The radars could interfere
with their electronic devices

00:29:01.390 --> 00:29:04.330 align:middle line:10%
and cause them to crash.

00:29:04.330 --> 00:29:07.360 align:middle line:84%
Many years before,
agent Guy Hottel

00:29:07.360 --> 00:29:09.880 align:middle line:84%
had become aware
of the crashed UFOs

00:29:09.880 --> 00:29:12.370 align:middle line:90%
in the vicinity of Los Alamos.

00:29:12.370 --> 00:29:16.240 align:middle line:84%
Hottel had informed J. Edgar
