of immune lymphatic cancer.

00:30:16.140 --> 00:30:18.850 align:middle line:10%


00:30:18.850 --> 00:30:22.290 align:middle line:10%
However, they were unable to
identify whether this tumorous

00:30:22.290 --> 00:30:27.030 align:middle line:10%
cancer was due to microwaves
or ionized radiation produced

00:30:27.030 --> 00:30:29.550 align:middle line:10%
by electronic devices.

00:30:29.550 --> 00:30:34.140 align:middle line:84%
This type of radar was
discontinued in 1957,

00:30:34.140 --> 00:30:37.770 align:middle line:84%
not only because they affected
the operator's health,

00:30:37.770 --> 00:30:42.390 align:middle line:84%
but because there was a
real danger to aviation.

00:30:42.390 --> 00:30:44.670 align:middle line:84%
There are unregistered
cases where

00:30:44.670 --> 00:30:47.730 align:middle line:84%
