a military nature,

00:30:47.730 --> 00:30:50.070 align:middle line:84%
crashed as a result
of the radars

00:30:50.070 --> 00:30:53.820 align:middle line:84%
interfering with their
navigation systems.

00:30:53.820 --> 00:30:55.440 align:middle line:84%
It was feared that
at any moment,

00:30:55.440 --> 00:30:58.170 align:middle line:84%
they could cause a commercial
airplane with passengers

00:30:58.170 --> 00:31:00.900 align:middle line:90%
on board to crash.

00:31:00.900 --> 00:31:03.930 align:middle line:84%
Little by little, we're
getting a better understanding

00:31:03.930 --> 00:31:09.240 align:middle line:84%
