with extraterrestrials

00:32:04.590 --> 00:32:08.360 align:middle line:84%
and we need to put some
protocols in place.

00:32:08.360 --> 00:32:10.788 align:middle line:84%
Because we're seeing
that they're coming.

00:32:10.788 --> 00:32:13.080 align:middle line:84%
This is Einstein and Oppenheimer
who wrote this letter.

00:32:13.080 --> 00:32:15.810 align:middle line:90%
It's in the MJ-12 documents.

00:32:15.810 --> 00:32:19.260 align:middle line:10%
>> A letter was written by
Albert Einstein and Robert

00:32:19.260 --> 00:32:23.280 align:middle line:10%
Oppenheimer to US
President Harry S. Truman.

00:32:23.280 --> 00:32:25.440 align:middle line:84%
