00:32:52.120 --> 00:32:54.190 align:middle line:84%
In principle, there
is no difficulty

00:32:54.190 --> 00:32:56.050 align:middle line:84%
in accepting the
possibility of coming

00:32:56.050 --> 00:32:59.050 align:middle line:84%
to an understanding with
