00:32:59.050 --> 00:33:01.300 align:middle line:90%
all kinds of relationships.

00:33:01.300 --> 00:33:04.060 align:middle line:84%
The difficulty lies
in trying to establish

00:33:04.060 --> 00:33:07.780 align:middle line:84%
the principles on which these
relationships should be based.

00:33:07.780 --> 00:33:10.720 align:middle line:84%
