00:33:13.990 --> 00:33:17.650 align:middle line:84%
and afterwards, as a first
condition for all intelligence,

00:33:17.650 --> 00:33:20.290 align:middle line:84%
that they should have a
psychology similar to that

00:33:20.290 --> 00:33:21.790 align:middle line:90%
of men.

00:33:21.790 --> 00:33:24.880 align:middle line:84%
At any rate, international
law should make place

00:33:24.880 --> 00:33:27.400 align:middle line:84%
for a new law on
a different basis.

00:33:27.400 --> 00:33:31.210 align:middle line:84%
And it might be called 'law
among planetary peoples.'

00:33:31.210 --> 00:33:34.240 align:middle line:84%
following the guidelines
found in the Pentateuch.

00:33:34.240 --> 00:33:36.670 align:middle line:10%
Obviously, the idea
of revolutionizing

00:33:36.670 --> 00:33:38.530 align:middle line:10%
international law to
the point to where

00:33:38.530 --> 00:33:41.650 align:middle line:10%
it would be capable of
coping with new situations

00:33:41.650 --> 00:33:44.740 align:middle line:10%
would compel us to make a
change in its structure,

00:33:44.740 --> 00:33:47.050 align:middle line:10%
a change so basic that
